Method Detail

setLoadImages

public static void setLoadImages(boolean b)
Switches automatic image data downloading on or off.

Parameters:
b - when set to true, the images are automatically loaded from the server. When set to false, the images are not loaded and the corresponding box is displayed empty. When the image loading is switched off, the box size can be only determined from the element attributes or style. The default value is on.
